    "en": {
      "title": "Degree courses from China for 18 Sri Lankan students",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China has arranged to award full scholarships to 18 Sri Lankan students. Thus, these scholarships have been awarded to 7 undergraduate students, 10 postgraduate students and one Ph.D.",
        "These students are going to study in 15 major universities in China. A scholarship awarding ceremony for the students was held under the chairmanship of Mr. Chi Shenhong, the Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka."
      ],
